c: 10
v: 4
t: "Ewuwe ni amulikalukha mwesi, indache ya Nyasaye eyatoto, toto ye niye wachachia ebiloonje naye khandi niye ulibikalusia, kho arunje balia basuubila mana nibakhola amalayi khubuleng’aafu. Ne balia bakhaya balinyoola ebinywebwa ebia amaatsi kayia pa nende eshinyasio eshilulu khulwa obukhayi bwabu"